Package ohos.account

Class DistributedInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.account.DistributedInfo

  • public class DistributedInfo
extends Object
    Provides methods for querying the distributed information of the OS account used for a distributed system, including the account ID and name. The distributed information refers to the account information that is used on a distributed network. It affects the availability of the distributed network and the distributed database.
    Since:
    1
